    dc:description "Figure 2. Lepisiota omanensis, sp. nov. (A) body in profile, (B) body in dorsal view, (C) body profile characters, (D) head in full-face view showing scape, and (E) head in full-face view showing clypeal and cephalic pilosity." ;
